					<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading mw-first-heading"><span class="mw-page-title-main">Hispanics in the American Civil War</span></h1>
							
<div id="p-lang-btn" class="vector-dropdown mw-portlet mw-portlet-lang"  >
