</li>
<li id="cite_note-46"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-46">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.homeofheroes.com/moh/citations_1862_cwh/ortega.html">Medal of Honor citation</a></span>
</li>
