</li>
<li id="cite_note-UoM-53"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-UoM_53-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-UoM_53-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://proust.library.miami.edu/findingaids/index.php?p=collections/findingaid&amp;id=57&amp;q=&amp;rootcontentid=6389">Fernando Fernández-Cavada Collection, 1846-1976 | University of Miami Cuban Heritage Collection</a></span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-54"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-54">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFHovey_(Public_Printer,_Santa_Fe)1860" class="citation web cs1">Hovey (Public Printer, Santa Fe), O.P (1860). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=1d5GAQAAIAAJ&amp;pg=PA110">"Laws passed by the General Assembly of the Territory of New Mexico"</a>. <i>New Mexico Territorial Laws [9th Assembly] 1859-'60</i>. State of New Mexico, 1860 Reprinted 1930<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">14 December</span> 2011</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=New+Mexico+Territorial+Laws+%5B9th+Assembly%5D+1859-%2760&amp;rft.atitle=Laws+passed+by+the+General+Assembly+of+the+Territory+of+New+Mexico&amp;rft.date=1860&amp;rft.aulast=Hovey+%28Public+Printer%2C+Santa+Fe%29&amp;rft.aufirst=O.P&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3D1d5GAQAAIAAJ%26pg%3DPA110&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AHispanics+in+the+American+Civil+War" class="Z3988"></span> p.110</span>
